Application Components Exported

Summary : It was found that some applications were using components with exported=true flag enabled.

OWASP Category: M3: 2016 Insecure Communication

Severity :   Medium  

Complexity : Easy 

From : Remote / External

Steps to Reproduce:

Proof of Concept : Attached in the Video


Impact : An Adversary can access and run the android components for malicious purposes.

Affected Path: Entire Application

Recommendations : Applications should make export=false and also remove Intent filters.
 
References : 
https://hackerone.com/reports/258460
https://hackerone.com/reports/161710
https://hackerone.com/reports/272044
https://hackerone.com/reports/289000
